sequenceDiagram
    participant C as MVNO Client
    participant CIF as CorrelationIdFilter
    participant ALF as AuditLogFilter
    participant AUTH as ApiKeyAuthFilter
    participant TIS as TenantIsolationService
    participant CTRL as DeviceCompatibilityController
    participant SVC as DeviceCompatibilityService
    participant BC as MvnoBandCatalogueService
    participant VC as VendorClient
    participant MET as Micrometer

    C->>CIF: GET /api/v1/devices/490154203237518/compatibility?mvno=mvno-a
    CIF->>CIF: Propagate / generate X-Correlation-ID
    CIF->>ALF: forward
    ALF->>AUTH: forward
    AUTH->>AUTH: resolve tenant=mvno-a from API key
    AUTH->>TIS: verify tenant mvno-a is active
    TIS-->>AUTH: OK
    AUTH->>CTRL: forward authenticated request

    CTRL->>CTRL: validate imei (15-digit pattern)
    CTRL->>CTRL: validate mvno (@NotBlank)
    CTRL->>SVC: checkCompatibility("490154203237518", "mvno-a")

    SVC->>TIS: assertIdentityMatch("mvno-a")
    TIS-->>SVC: OK

    SVC->>VC: fetchDeviceDetails("490154203237518", "mvno-a")
    VC-->>SVC: VendorDeviceResponse{supportedBands: ["B1","B3","B7","B20","B28"]}

    SVC->>BC: getRequiredBands("mvno-a")
    BC-->>SVC: ["B1","B3","B7","B20"]

    SVC->>SVC: matchedBands = intersection → ["B1","B3","B7","B20"]
    SVC->>SVC: compatible = matchedBands ⊇ requiredBands → true
    SVC->>MET: device.compatibility.check.compatible++
    SVC->>ALF: outcome=COMPATIBLE
    ALF->>ALF: write audit log (tenant=mvno-a, imei=****7518, outcome=COMPATIBLE)

    SVC-->>CTRL: DeviceCompatibilityResponse{compatible=true, matchedBands=[...]}
    CTRL-->>C: HTTP 200 {imei, mvno, compatible:true, supportedBands, requiredBands, matchedBands}

    Note over C,MET: Incompatible device path
    C->>SVC: checkCompatibility("352000000000001", "mvno-a")
    SVC->>VC: fetchDeviceDetails(...)
    VC-->>SVC: VendorDeviceResponse{supportedBands: ["B1","B3"]}
    SVC->>BC: getRequiredBands("mvno-a")
    BC-->>SVC: ["B1","B3","B7","B20"]
    SVC->>SVC: matchedBands=["B1","B3"], compatible=false, reason="Missing bands: B7, B20"
    SVC->>MET: device.compatibility.check.incompatible++
    SVC-->>CTRL: DeviceCompatibilityResponse{compatible=false, reason="Missing bands: B7, B20"}
    CTRL-->>C: HTTP 200 {compatible:false, reason:"Missing bands: B7, B20"}

    Note over C,MET: Vendor unavailable path
    C->>SVC: checkCompatibility("...", "mvno-a")
    SVC->>VC: fetchDeviceDetails(...)
    VC-->>SVC: VendorUnavailableException
    SVC->>MET: device.compatibility.check.vendor_error++
    SVC-->>CTRL: throws VendorUnavailableException
    CTRL-->>C: HTTP 503 Retry-After: 30
